		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之冰在近身处刺出数个冰刺，有单边展开和双边合拢两种方式，均造成<span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
